data.description: Situated in prime location & close proximity to Interstate 65, this full-brick residence offers both comfort and convenience. Boasting three spacious bedrooms, including a master suite, full bath and an additional half bath for guests, this home is designed for both relaxation and entertainment. The heart of the home lies in its large kitchen, complete with a breakfast bar and an inviting eat-in area. Perfect for family gatherings and hosting friends. Hardwood floors throughout add a touch of elegance to the living spaces, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Large laundry room with ample space for extra freezers and storage. Two covered porches beckon you to embrace the outdoors, while the basement features a versatile office/den, ideal for remote work or a cozy retreat.One-car garage in the basement. The fenced yard offers privacy and safety for family and pets. Additional outdoor spaces include a covered deck & carport awning. Schedule a viewing of this exceptional home today!
